      "type": "qa",
      "text": "> 💬 Practice tip: Say each answer OUT LOUD. Target 60–90 seconds per answer. Q: Explain cloud computing to a non-technical executive. Q: What is the Shared Responsibility Model? Where do most breaches happen? Q: Why would a company NOT move to cloud? Q: Is multi-tenancy safe? My code runs on the same hardware as other companies? Q: What are the 5 characteristics of cloud and can you give an example that violates each? ---"
